    "Details": "An anti-aircraft model based on the XS, the XX mounts a Mydron Excel LB 10-X autocannon in place of the standard model. While carrying two tons of ammunition, the designers were not able to adapt the ammo feed to switch between ammo types, forcing the XX to carry either standard or cluster ammunition in battle\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Modular Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
